headline: Why Lululemon Will Avoid Trump’s Tariffs and Canada Goose Might Not
summary: Lululemon  leggings won’t cost more, but  Canada Goose  parkas might.  The U.S. tariffs on Canada—now partly on hold for a month—haven’t hit all Canadian companies equally.  Lululemon Athletica and Canada Goose are both based in Canada.
